    "default_locale": "en-US",
    "description": {
        "en-US": "Mailbox Alert allows you to specify, for each separate mail folder, a message, sound and/or a system command that will be executed when new mail is found there. \n\nThis way, you specify different actions for less important folders, or no action at all.\n\nDue to the individual folder (or filter) settings, the plugin is configurable with a right-click on an account or folder, not in the main preferences window. Please read <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://outgoing.prod.mozaws.net/v1/afc64dce30bf101355e332e6884d4bd8f3636ea94b32259abcc1b4464031ba4e/https%3A//tjeb.nl/Projects/Mailbox_Alert/Manual/\">https://tjeb.nl/Projects/Mailbox_Alert/Manual/</a> for more information and examples.\n\nAdditionally, while I haven't spent much time on it lately, please send bug reports to me directly. A negative review is fine, but I cannot engage to get bugs fixed through reviews :)"
    },
